GalaxyMage Redux: an open-source tactical RPG.
http://galaxymage.brandonbarnes.us/

Copyright (c) 2007 Brandon Barnes <freelance.brandon@yahoo.com> and 
contributors.

INSTALLATION

Galaxy Mage Redux is written in Python, so you will need a Python
interpreter to run it.  You will also need several Python modules.

* Python
  http://python.org

* PyOpenGL
  http://pyopengl.sourceforge.net

* PyGame
  http://pygame.org

* Twisted
  http://twistedmatrix.com

After everything is installed properly you should be able run the game
by typing

$ python GalaxyMage.py

into a terminal or by double clicking GalaxyMage.py in a graphical file
manager.

